            "textentryhtml":"Round, 4.65 cm. diam. (warm-ish) silver head-to-collar Mao floating slightly above center against a vermillion ground; below Mao = the top of a globe with clearly defined longitude & latitude lines, with approximately 9 flags in front of it; this is bordered at the base of the badge by an unfurled ribbon that goes beyond the outer edge; inscription across the middle: “世界进入了毛泽东思想伟大新时代”.\r\nBack: some red enamel smudged at top & bottom; head-shaped indetation; clasp = at eye level  Below clasp = “忠” ; below indentation = 2-line inscription: “永远忠于毛主席” / “121 部队”.\r\n\r\n",
